%H A299900 Reticular Chemistry Structure Resource (RCSR), <a href="http://rcsr.net/nets/ftu">The ftu tiling (or net)</a>
%F A299900 The following is a conjectured recurrence, found by gfun, using the command rec:=gfun[listtorec](t1, a(n)); (where t1 is a list of the initial terms) suggested by _Paul Zimmermann_.
%F A299900 Note: this should not be used to extend the sequence.
%F A299900 0 = 10*a(n+28)-9*a(n+29)+8*a(n+30)-7*a(n+31)+7*a(n+32)-8*a(n+33)+9*a(n+34) -10*a(n+35)+10*a(n+36)-10*a(n+37)+9*a(n+38)-9*a(n+39) +9*a(n+40) -10*a(n+41)+10*a(n+42)-10*a(n+43)+9*a(n+44)-9*a(n+45)+9*a(n+46)
%F A299900 -9*a(n+47)+8*a(n+48)-7*a(n+49)+6*a(n+50)-5*a(n+51)+4*a(n+52) -3*a(n+53)+3*a(n+54) -3*a(n+55)+3*a(n+56)-2*a(n+57)+a(n+58)+10*a(n+20)-10*a(n+21)-a(n+5)+2*a(n+6)-3*a(n+7)+3*a(n+8)-3*a(n+9)+3*a(n+10) -4*a(n+11
